text: Season 1889–90 was the 14th season in which Hibernian competed at a Scottish national level, entering the Scottish Cup for the 13th time. == Overview == Hibs reached the sixth round of the Scottish Cup, losing 6–2 to Abercorn. == Results == All results are written with Hibs' score first. === Scottish Cup === {| class="wikitable sortable" style="font-size:100%; text-align:center" !Date!!Round!!Opponent!!Venue!!Result!!Attendance!!Scorers |- bgcolor = "#eeffee" | 7 September 1889||R1||Armadale||A||3–2|||| |- bgcolor = "#eeffee" | 28 September 1889||R2||Mossend Swifts||H||4–3||2,500|| |- bgcolor = "#fffdd" | 19 October 1889||R3||Dunfermline Athletic||A||4–4|||| |- bgcolor = "#eeffee" | 26 October 1889||R3 R||Dunfermline Athletic||H||11–1||2,000|| |- bgcolor = "#eeffee" | 9 November 1889||R4||Queen of the South Wanderers||A||7–3|||| |- bgcolor = "#eeffee" | 30 November 1889||R5||Bye in Round 6|||||||| |- bgcolor = "#ffeeee" | 21 December 1889||R6||Abercorn||A||2–6||4,500|| |} ==See also== *List of Hibernian F.C. seasons == Notes == == External links == * Results For Season 1889/1890 in All Competitions, www.ihibs.co.uk Category:Hibernian F.C. seasons Hibernian
